hopobject.body: What are the hours of work? star combo pharma limited prospectus Elvis Presley's granddaughter, Riley Keough, is the new face of Lee jeans. Keough rocks some Lee denim in the new campaign titled 'A Lee Don't Lie.' Keough is a third generation celebrity and is the daughter of Lisa Marie Presley and Danny Keough. She's the oldest grandchild of Elvis and Priscilla Presley and is making a name for herself with high-profile modeling jobs.
